node.text: It’s crazy how Dino becomes the fastest tortoise on the west coast  when offered watermelon yet Wilbur still sucks at eating but can escape like a true pro and yes he would bite me if I let him, luckily his aim is way off 😂 #tortoisesofinstagram #sulcatatortoise #rescue #DinoLasek #wilburlasek

Where’s my Denver people at?? I’m bringing my Rally car for the Rally Sprint @gridlifeofficial #GRIDLIFE Alpine Horizon which starts TOMORROW‼️‼️ Join us for 3 EPIC days with music from @suicideboys | @lupefiasco | @flosstradamus | @yunggravy | @ramirez_187 | @bobbysessionstx & more! And driving from @ryantuerck | @chrisforsberg64 | @vaughngittinjr | @chelseadenofa | @mattfield777 | @justinpawlak13 | @daiyoshihara | @michaelessa | @adam_lz | @deankarnage | @ryanlitteral | @dirk_stratton | @modifiedperformance | @coreyhosford | @joshrobinson530 | @loren_healy | @garrett_1320video | @tjhunt_ | @dustiinw | @buckylasek | @chris_jeanneret | @texas_dave | @shredderracing | @motionautotv & more! Its all going down at @ppir! Last chance to secure tickets beforehand! Tickets available in @gridlifeofficial @alpinehorizonfest BIO🔥

#GRIDLIFEAlpine | #GRIDLIFEDrift | #ColoradoSprings | #PPIR
